      },
      "date": "2012-08-09 09:47:46.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3: I would prefer that you didn't submit this\n\nLooking at this more closely, it is changing only osd_ldiskfs_writelink(), but the problem happens with long symlinks, so I don't think this is actually fixing the bug, AFAICS. \n\nThis would be much better if it included the regression test from LU-1540, which would let us know for sure whether this code will fix the problem.",
